# Intent
  (none)

# Helpers
  @fn twoSendersOneTrack(opts)  @ 12-36
      -- Stage-2 fixture: two source-tracks each midi-sending into trackKey-c, hitting
      -- a distinct terminal-consumer JSFX. fxC2 ends up on bus 1 (fxC1 holds bus 0).

# Cases
  @case 'midi bracket: terminal consumer on bus N≠0 parks on 127 and swallows its out'  [pure]  @ 40-53
  @case 'midi bracket: bus-0 consumer needs only the out-blocker'  [pure]  @ 56-72
  @case 'midi bracket: busAware JSFX is never bracketed (refusal upstream is bypassed here)'  [pure]  @ 75-82
  @case 'midi bracket: non-JSFX fx is never bracketed (VST bus filter is its own slice)'  [pure]  @ 85-92
  @case 'midi bracket: consumer-producer JSFX routes its emission to the allocated out bus'  [pure]  @ 95-137
  @case 'midi bracket: disconnected midi-in JSFX is silenced; bus-0 stream crosses intact'  [pure]  @ 140-162
  @case 'midi bracket: pure-audio JSFX (scanned midi 0/0) is never bracketed'  [pure]  @ 165-182
  @case 'midi bracket: send-only JSFX parks the crossing stream before taking its out bus'  [pure]  @ 185-215
  @case 'midi bracket: bracket pinMaps pass audio identity on pair 1'  [pure]  @ 218-226
  @case 'midi bracket: same input → same output (determinism)'  [pure]  @ 229-236

